Introduction

KARDI is a four-member project co-ed rock band. Originally as five, they were formed through JTBC's survival show SuperBand 2 and finished in 3rd place on the show in 2021.

They released their 1st mini album "Chil" on September 25, 2022.

On March 20, 2023, it was announced that drummer Jeon Seongbae would be leaving with his last live performance as a member being their concert held on April 12, 2023. His last drum session recording for KARDI was featured on their studio album "Inside Out" that was released on July 17, 2023.
